{"snp4.8:0.1":"Sutta Nipata 4.8 ","snp4.8:0.2":"Pasurasutta ","snp4.8:1.1":"Idheva suddhi iti vadayanti, ","snp4.8:1.2":"Nannesu dhammesu visuddhimahu; ","snp4.8:1.3":"Yam nissita tattha subham vadana, ","snp4.8:1.4":"Paccekasaccesu puthu nivittha. ","snp4.8:2.1":"Te vadakama parisam vigayha, ","snp4.8:2.2":"Balam dahanti mithu annamannam; ","snp4.8:2.3":"Vadanti te annasita kathojjam, ","snp4.8:2.4":"Pasamsakama kusala vadana. ","snp4.8:3.1":"Yutto kathayam parisaya majjhe, ","snp4.8:3.2":"Pasamsamiccham vinighati hoti; ","snp4.8:3.3":"Apahatasmim pana manku hoti, ","snp4.8:3.4":"Nindaya so kuppati randhamesi. ","snp4.8:4.1":"Yamassa vadam parihinamahu, ","snp4.8:4.2":"Apahatam panhavimamsakase; ","snp4.8:4.3":"Paridevati socati hinavado, ","snp4.8:4.4":"Upaccaga manti anutthunati. ","snp4.8:5.1":"Ete vivada samanesu jata, ","snp4.8:5.2":"Etesu ugghatinighati hoti; ","snp4.8:5.3":"Etampi disva virame kathojjam, ","snp4.8:5.4":"Na hannadatthatthi pasamsalabha. ","snp4.8:6.1":"Pasamsito va pana tattha hoti, ","snp4.8:6.2":"Akkhaya vadam parisaya majjhe; ","snp4.8:6.3":"So hassati unnamati ca tena, ","snp4.8:6.4":"Pappuyya tamattham yatha mano ahu. ","snp4.8:7.1":"Ya unnati sassa vighatabhumi, ","snp4.8:7.2":"Manatimanam vadate paneso; ","snp4.8:7.3":"Etampi disva na vivadayetha, ","snp4.8:7.4":"Na hi tena suddhim kusala vadanti. ","snp4.8:8.1":"Suro yatha rajakhadaya puttho, ","snp4.8:8.2":"Abhigajjameti patisuramiccham; ","snp4.8:8.3":"Yeneva so tena palehi sura, ","snp4.8:8.4":"Pubbeva natthi yadidam yudhaya. ","snp4.8:9.1":"Ye ditthimuggayha vivadayanti, ","snp4.8:9.2":"Idameva saccanti ca vadayanti; ","snp4.8:9.3":"Te tvam vadassu na hi tedha atthi, ","snp4.8:9.4":"Vadamhi jate patisenikatta. ","snp4.8:10.1":"Visenikatva pana ye caranti, ","snp4.8:10.2":"Ditthihi ditthim avirujjhamana; ","snp4.8:10.3":"Tesu tvam kim labhetho pasura, ","snp4.8:10.4":"Yesidha natthi paramuggahitam. ","snp4.8:11.1":"Atha tvam pavitakkamagama, ","snp4.8:11.2":"Manasa ditthigatani cintayanto; ","snp4.8:11.3":"Dhonena yugam samagama, ","snp4.8:11.4":"Na hi tvam sakkhasi sampayataveti. ","snp4.8:11.5":"Pasurasuttam atthamam. "}